        <updateDate>2019-09-05T15:47:02Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>EAGLES Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill provides statutory authority for the National Threat Assessment Center (NTAC) within the Department of Homeland Security. </p> <p>It authorizes the functions of NTAC through FY2022 and expands them to include the establishment of a national program on targeted school violence prevention. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
